Murray Matheson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Murray_Matheson 0 Sidney Murray Matheson (1 July 1912 – 25 April 1985) was an American-based Australian actor. He appeared on stage and in films and television programs until 1983. Sidney_Murray_Matheson ( 1_July_1912 – 25_April_1985 ) was an_American-based_Australian_actor . He appeared on stage and in films_and_television_programs until 1983 .
